OL,3,CFirst trailer released for returning
OL,4,CJersey detective drama Bergerac
OL,6,FFans of the Jersey detective show
OL,7,FBergerac will not have to wait much
OL,8,Flonger for new episodes, as producers
OL,9,Fhave confirmed that it is returning to
OL,10,Fscreens "soon".
OL,12,FAlthough an exact date has not yet
OL,13,Fbeen publicised, UKTV has released a
OL,14,Fteaser video and says the new series
OL,15,Fwill be broadcast on streaming
OL,16,Fplatform U, plus the channel U&DRAMA,
OL,17,Fthis spring.
