OL,3,CFirst trailer released for returning
OL,4,CJersey detective drama Bergerac
OL,6,FThe trailer shows Jim Bergerac, played
OL,7,Fby Damien Molony, struggling to
OL,8,Fmaintain control as a voiceover says,
OL,9,F"Jim, you're this great detective, but
OL,10,Fyou're impulsive and that makes you
OL,11,Fdangerous to be around".
OL,13,FIt continues: "You're cavalier and
OL,14,Farrogant. You have no discipline."
OL,16,FMolony will be joined by returning
OL,17,Fstar Zoe Wanamaker, who plays his
OL,18,Fmother Charlie Hungerford, and several
OL,19,Fnew faces - including actors Lesley
OL,20,FSharp and Adrian Edmondson.
